00:21:58.640 --> 00:21:59.640
Tú…

00:22:00.704 --> 00:22:01.728
Te lo advierto.

00:22:02.479 --> 00:22:03.760
Ya no puedes vencerme.

00:22:05.479 --> 00:22:07.060
